description_buyer: Back in the 70's there was a marvelous second-hand store on 13th Street close to MacDonald Avenue in Richmond called Value Village. One day I was shopping there in the upstairs loft area and came upon a filthy canvas covered box. Ill-concealing my contempt, I kicked it and it skittered across the floor. Intrigued, I opened it up and discovered a rattan trunk from the South Pacific and World War II. I stripped off the canvas and revealed what you see in these photos.
description_seller: Back in the 70's there was a marvelous second-hand store on 13th Street close to MacDonald Avenue in Richmond called Value Village. One day I was shopping there in the upstairs loft area and came upon a filthy canvas covered box. Ill-concealing my contempt, I kicked it and it skittered across the floor. Intrigued, I opened it up and discovered a rattan trunk from the South Pacific and World War II. I stripped off the canvas and revealed what you see in these photos. We have used it since as a coffee table, for linen storage and as a laundry bin. It's a very versatile piece of furniture and is lightweight. It has nice, chunky, heavy-duty brass hardware. Dimensions: 39 " long 25" wide 19" tall

scenario_title: Antique bureau w/ mirror + stained glass
description_buyer: This beautiful bureau is made entirely of wood with lovely accents and details, a nice curving front, stained glass cabinets, an inside light behind the stained glass, and a removable top with mirror and extra shelves. The whole thing is gorgeous and wonderfully preserved, with no scratches and no stains. The one flaw is that one of the draw handles lost its screw. We still have the porcelain handle, but to reattach you'd need to find the right screw.
description_seller: This beautiful bureau is made entirely of wood with lovely accents and details, a nice curving front, stained glass cabinets, an inside light behind the stained glass, and a removable top with mirror and extra shelves. It's also good for displaying things, as it has an open top shelf. Despite its size, it's not as heavy as you'd think. You will have to pick up, but I can help carry.

scenario_title: Dining Table and 8 Chairs-Beautiful Vintage Mid Century Rattan Bamboo
description_buyer: Kalp - Son Rattan Co 11 piece Dining Set for sale. Quality real furniture!  Just in time for the Holidays,  feast and Christmas gatherings. Expands to hold 8 people, collapses to 4 people, apartment sized or formal dining room sized.  Mid Century Hollywood Regency style,  Kalp - Son Rattan Co. aqua/teal vinyl covered real Bamboo Chairs and Bamboo dining table for sale.  The dining Table is 48" round and expands up to 82" oblong when the two 17" leaves are added. (28" high) Chairs seat height is 17"  height of chair back is 28" high, seat is 16" wide.  Some of the chairs can use some stitching, but are in overall beautiful condition.  Please see the pictures.  You can use them now as they are or re-cover them.  These pieces stand the test of time and will last for a very long time to come.   I am asking 1200.00 for the entire set.  If interested, please call, do not text.  Local pick up, cash only.  If the ad is up, it's available

scenario_title: West Elm Henry 96" sofa couch new
description_buyer: I have a new West Elm Henry 96" sofa couch in Tweed, Salt + Pepper for sale. Bought it and it wasn't a good fit. It is brand new and never used. Sample fabric is as shown in the picture. Picture 1 - 6 is stock picture. Picture 7 and 8 is actual photo of the sofa / couch. Specs: Now available in Grand sizing, the Henry Sofa is a comfortable classic that's always in style. Each is crafted with hand-built frames, hand-finished upholstery and many recycled materials.
description_seller: I have a new West Elm Henry 96" sofa couch in Tweed, Salt + Pepper for sale. Bought it and it wasn't a good fit. It is brand new and never used. Sample fabric is as shown in the picture. Picture 1 - 6 is stock picture. Picture 7 and 8 is actual photo of the sofa / couch. Specs: Now available in Grand sizing, the Henry Sofa is a comfortable classic that's always in style. Each is crafted with hand-built frames, hand-finished upholstery and many recycled materials. Loose cushions with foam padding for maximum comfort. Solid wood legs with Chocolate-stained finish. Seat deck and springs made from 70% recycled materials. Foam in cushions and arms made from 20% soy-based materials. Pillow filling made from recycled water bottles; padding and seat fiber made from recycled carpet materials.

scenario_title: TWO Vermont Furniture Designs cherry wood dressers
description_buyer: For Sale:  TWO Vermont Furniture Designs cherry wood dressers.  Beautiful craftsmanship and solidly built.  This is not your IKEA particle board throw-away junk!  These will last for years and become heirlooms for you to pass down.
description_seller: For Sale:  TWO Vermont Furniture Designs cherry wood dressers.  Beautiful craftsmanship and solidly built.  This is not your IKEA particle board throw-away junk!  These will last for years and become heirlooms for you to pass down. These are in good shape but not perfect - they were in our kids room.  There are some surface level scratches on the top and some marks in various places.  They look beautiful as they are, and if you were really motivated you could sand and oil the top to bring them back to perfect.  They are not museum pieces, but rather an amazing value on expensive, quality, solid furniture. Please email with questions.  Thanks for looking!

scenario_title: Mid Century Modern MCM side table / nigthstand
description_buyer: The details on this midcentury piece combine to turn an ordinary nightstand into something more understated. The subtle taper of the legs draw inspiration from 60's Danish design and the drawer pull is framed with an elegant wooden feature. Coasters won't be needed in the company of this piece as the top has a layer of formica protecting it. Bears the usual dings and scratches near the bottom of the legs that a well-loved side table would. Features the Lane logo on the botton and inside of the drawer. This vintage mid-century modern walnut piece can be use as a coffee table / side table / nightstand and will bring sophisticated style to any space.  Features a lower shelf for additional storage.

description_buyer: This premium Sealy Francisco Plush is an excellent mattress that is ideal for just about any type of sleeper. Overall, if you're in the market for a mattress that's going to provide conforming, yet firm comfort, this Sealy mattress is a good way to go. Used by child so no sagging and no stains or smells because always covered with protective waterproof sheets. Just used for 2.5 years old.

scenario_title: Vintage Singer Sewing Machine Lift PN# 124384
description_buyer: For use with Models:  15, 66, 28, 27, 15-91, 201 Used, vintage items showing normal wear & tear from age & use. See photos for condition of finish. There may be some tarnish, discoloration, rust, pits, scratches, dents or flaking plating/paint. Cast-iron Machine Lift. 4-Screw, offest rib "V" mount.  Includes mounting screws & limit chain.
description_seller: For use with Models:  15, 66, 28, 27, 15-91, 201 Used, vintage items showing normal wear & tear from age & use. See photos for condition of finish. There may be some tarnish, discoloration, rust, pits, scratches, dents or flaking plating/paint. Cast-iron Machine Lift. 4-Screw, offest rib "V" mount.  Includes mounting screws & limit chain. Strong Spring, Right-Hand thread on stud & nut. Approx 1-1/2" offset from mounting plate to top of lift plate. This unit is designed to mount to the underside of a 1-1/2" thick top with a beveled support rib.  Typically this particular mount was used on the older treadle machines with the cast-iron bases and not on the more modern wood cabinets. This unit is in Very Good condition with glossy black japan finish and no significant chips or scratches.

description_buyer: For sale is a big ikea sleeper sofa, similar to this one http://www.ikea.com/us/en/catalog/products/S99150750/. Dimensions are 28.75"H x 94.5"W x 35.5"D Seat & Bed height 17.75''. It converts into about a queen-sized bed. It also has a very convenient storage place where we keep bedding supplies.
description_seller: For sale is a big ikea sleeper sofa, similar to this one http://www.ikea.com/us/en/catalog/products/S99150750/. Dimensions are 28.75"H x 94.5"W x 35.5"D Seat & Bed height 17.75''. It converts into about a queen-sized bed. It also has a very convenient storage place where we keep bedding supplies. Overall the sofa is in a good shape, no pets/smokers in the household. There is a bit of fading of fabrics (clearly visible on picture where it is converted into a bed) otherwise fabrics is in a good shape. Note the orientation of the corner, I believe it cannot be changed. Cash only. It disassembles into three pieces, plus three pillows. I am happy to disassemble it for you and help to carry it to your car.  Also, I can deliver within 5 mile radius for an extra 50$.
